Package com.microsoft.azure.management.websites

This package contains the websites management class, interface, and associated configuration and utility classes.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    SourceControlOperations
    User source controls operations
    WebHostingPlanOperations
    Operations for managing the Web Hosting Plans in a resource group.
    WebSiteManagementClient
    The Windows Azure Web Sites management API provides a RESTful set of web services that interact with Windows Azure Web Sites service to manage your web sites.
    WebSiteOperations
    Operations for managing the web sites in a web space.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Exports
    The Class Exports.
    SourceControlOperationsImpl
    User source controls operations
    WebHostingPlanOperationsImpl
    Operations for managing the Web Hosting Plans in a resource group.
    WebSiteExtendedErrorCodes
    In addition to standard HTTP status codes, the Windows Azure Web Sites Management REST API returns extended error codes and error messages.
    WebSiteManagementClientImpl
    The Windows Azure Web Sites management API provides a RESTful set of web services that interact with Windows Azure Web Sites service to manage your web sites.
    WebSiteManagementService
    Access service management functionality.
    WebSiteOperationsImpl
    Operations for managing the web sites in a web space.
